OL,3,CWho knew what? A timeline of events in
OL,4,Cthe Church of England abuse scandal
OL,6,FThe Archbishop of Canterbury Justin
OL,7,FWelby has resigned over his handling
OL,8,Fof the John Smyth abuse case, after
OL,9,Ffacing mounting pressure to step down.
OL,11,FSmyth abused young boys at Christian
OL,12,Fsummer camps, and is thought to have
OL,13,Fbeen the most prolific abuser
OL,14,Fassociated with the Church of England.
OL,15,FHe died in 2018 whilst under
OL,16,Finvestigation by Hampshire Police.
OL,18,FThree members of the Church's
OL,19,Fparliament, the General Synod, claim
OL,20,Fthe archbishop was aware of Smyth's
OL,21,Fcrimes.
